snippet.title: Spike Volleyball | Motion Capture : The Serve
snippet.description:
The serve is absolutely key in indoor volleyball, learn how Black Sheep Studio made it as realistic as possible through motion-capture.

🗓️ Spike Volleyball will be available on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and PC starting February 5th, 2019!
